{
  "text": "Equal volumes (5 μl) of 17 μM gst-IGD-flag and 1 nM ADAMTS-4 which lacks the C-terminal spacer domain (ADAMTS-4-2 [CITATION_1] ) or 0.5 nM ADAMTS-5 which lacks the C-terminal cysteine-rich spacer and thrombospondin domains (ADAMTS-5-4 [CITATION_2] ) were incubated at 37",
  "correct_citation": {
